    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Term formerly used for a variety of bedcovers, especially those woven of cotton or wool; from the mid-19th century onwards generally replaced by the term "bedspreads."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
